data.description: Great opportunity to restore this light cosmetic fixer situated at the end of a cul-de-sac in the Beard's Cove community where members enjoy access to the private beach, boat launch, the clubhouse and pool. Functional floorplan with open living room, dining room and kitchen space with breakfast bar.  Attached 1 Car Garage. Newer Roof. Close to town, shopping, schools, parks and Hwy 3. Great commute to PSNS, Bangor & Keyport.
